ould focus on EQT=E2=80=99s existing investors. The private transaction wou=
ld give investors in the private company the ability to sell shares, or sim=
ply hold them. Others would get the chance to buy.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So it=E2=80=99s like an IPO, except that inste=
ad of marketing the shares to everyone, you market them only to existing cl=
ients of EQT? Why would that get a better price?</p>
